commitResults.messageTitle: Rename NusmodCommand to ShowNusModCommand *  Add POJOs corresponding to NUSMods Json data * Add NusModsApiParser to parse Json data from NusModsApi to POJOs * Fix ShowNusModCommand * Add NusModsData class to group NUSMods-related data for use in ModelManager * Add ApiCache skeleton to support api caching in future * Add AppSettings and for UserPrefs * Add NUSModShareLink model for future use
Fix ShowNusMod feature and many module-related adjustments (#84)
commitResults.messageBody:
* Rename NusmodCommand to ShowNusModCommand
*  Add POJOs corresponding to NUSMods Json data
* Add NusModApiParser to parse Json data from NusModApi to POJOs
* Fix ShowNusModCommand
* Add NusModsData class to group NUSMods-related data for use in ModelManager
* Add ApiCache skeleton to support api caching in future
* Add AppSettings and for UserPrefs
* Add NUSModShareLink model for future use
* Improve code quality
* Rename NusModApi/NusModApiParser to NusModsApi/NusModsApiParser

commitResults.messageBody: Java's Double.MIN_VALUE represents the smallest positive number (e.g. 0.00000[...]1) instead of the smallest absolute number (e.g. -999[...].999[...]).
